    "Furthermore, new sophisticated technologies, such as Software Defined Networking (SDN) and Network Function Virtualization (NFV), have evolved to support the integration of AI techniques with enhanced and elastic 1 3 anomaly detection mechanisms (Papavassiliou 2020).",
    "These are programmable and flexible technologies that can plug into AI-based anomaly detection which needs an integrated and real-time perception of the network hardware architecture (Schmitt 2023).",
